node.text: This one is for all the young hoopers out there! We hope that by listening to our journey from AAU to the NBA you can get some insight into how our mindsets grew and shifted to help us be where we’re at. Thank you to my brother @traeyoung for this conversation! @curiousmike episode 2 out now

node.text: I sat down to explain to everyone what @curiousmike is going to be! Link in my bio to watch on YouTube or listen as a podcast. Excited to share these conversations with @lecrae @traeyoung @judahsmith and my Great Aunt Nancy. Season 1 soon ⏳
